            "title": "九龍灣垃圾車冒煙  途人報警",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"垃圾車車尾冒煙。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f97f4d703a8b0df0eab1d098c9e3f16e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051515404241388.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">垃圾車車尾冒煙。fb：車cam L（香港群組）</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（15日）午3時21分，一輛垃圾車沿九龍灣常悅道行駛，在環球工商大廈對開時，車尾突然冒出濃煙，途人見狀報警，消防趕赴現場。 \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250032/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"垃圾車冒煙。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/422a213529aaf4238a940f1059b19a58/2025-05/01_1_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        垃圾車冒煙。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
